    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "If we used sys.prefix, we'd need to be very careful and have quite a few special cases, because it often has the wrong value on OS X (/System/Library/... or /Library/... or /usr/local/Cellar/...) and debian (/usr), in all of which cases kernelspecs should go in /usr/local. It's also the wrong thing to use on Windows.\n"
